            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>INTEGRITY_VIOLATION</td>
              <td><span data-level="error">ERROR</span></td>
              <td>SHA-256 of the downloaded asset does not match the manifest or pin. Halts rendering in EXECUTED.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td>PINNED_FONT_UNAVAILABLE</td>
              <td><span data-level="error">ERROR</span></td>
